## SETTING UP ENVIRONMENT
```{r setup}

library(gt)
library(skimr)
library(lubridate)
library(tidytuesdayR)
```

## IMPORTING THE DATA
```{r}
tuesdata <- tidytuesdayR::tt_load(2022, week = 8)

freedom <- tuesdata$freedom
freedom
```
